# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in git, regardless of the
# contributor's platform or core.autocrlf setting. Prevents CRLF churn and
# keeps tools like gofmt from flagging every file on Windows checkouts.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly binary so git never touches their bytes.
*.exe   binary
*.wasm  binary
*.png   binary
*.ico   binary
*.zip   binary
